              "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
            },
            "body": "Excellent idea. That's something we've been kicking around for a while.  YARN-5139 proposes that model for the capacity scheduler.  Have a look at the specs there for a sense of scope.",
            "updateAuthor": {
              "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=templedf",
              "name": "templedf",
              "key": "templedf",
              "avatarUrls": {
