            },
            "body": "[~kasha] thank you for sharing your comment.\nI try to do like that, we compute resource deficit for every app considering policies in updateThread. In the list of apps maintained, we sort apps by the amount of resource deficit.  And generally we try to assign container to apps with the most resource deficit in each nodeUpdate.",
